title: A home you can settle in at - Res Lease in Pflugerville. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['This lovely 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is waiting for you to lease!', 'Located in Pflugerville, TX and in close proximity to parks, pools, and entertainment!', "Entering the front door, you'll find the living space and a fully equipped kitchen featuring tile flooring, granite countertops, stainless appliances, and subway tile backsplash with white cabinets.", 'The bedrooms are spacious and luminous, all with carpeted flooring.', 'The main bedroom has a full bathroom with double vanity and a walk-in closet.', 'The private back yard with its beautiful lawn where nice afternoons will be great with some friends over or just to relax after a long day at work!', 'Tour and apply to this one before it’s gone!', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package', '**', 'Home must be toured in person, no exceptions', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 2452076)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
